Contact Us
Please let us know how we can assist you. Thank you for your interest in American Electric Power.
If you have a question, comment, or wish to report a problem with this web site, please choose from among the options below so we may handle your communication most efficiently.



Outages & Safety Hazards




								Please report safety hazards immediately to our Customer Solutions Center at 800-277-2177 (24 hours/day).

You can report an outage online.




