Life At AEP

Required Testing

				Read our Employment Testing and Information Tips (provided by Edison Electric
				Institute) if you are applying for any of the following positions:
			

Clerical or administrative support
Meter reading
Plant operation or maintenance
Distribution or transmission construction


Troubleshooting

If you are having trouble viewing jobs, read
					our troubleshooting tips. 
If, after reading our troubleshooting tips, you're still having technical trouble, please e-mail us at 
					HRISRecruitHelp@aep.com.









