Think Inside The Box
Offering a Complete Line of DIN Rail Mounted Products, For Less
We offer a complete line of DIN Rail mounted components – Including Terminal Blocks, Power Supplies, Fuse Holders, Circuit Breakers, Interface Modules and Disconnect Switches.  We also sell Printed Circuit Board Terminals and Connectors, Wire Ferrules and Tools for Crimping Ferrules and Cable Grips.






DIN Rail Mounted Terminal Blocks

American Electrical offers the complete line of Klemsan,   Internationally approved and recognized, DIN Rail mounted terminal   blocks.

                                  Additional information can be obtained from the Klemsan website   at Klemsan



DIN Rail Mounted Circuit Breakers, MCCB's and Contactors

American Electrical offers the thinnest DIN Rail mounted   Circuit Breaker on the market (13mm). Available in UL 1077, UL 489 and UL 489A –   AC and DC versions.



DIN Rail Mounted Fuse Holders

American Electrical offers fuse holders for applications up to   50 amps in five different fuse types (English and Metric)




DIN Rail Mounted Power Supplies

American Electrical offers two lines of DIN Rail mounted Power   Supplies, from 1.875 amps to 40 amps – 24VDC outputs and 120-480VAC inputs,   single and three phase.


Wire Ferrules

American Electrical has the widest line of Wire Ferrules in   North America – all colors, all sizes – and make sure you check out the tools we   offer to go with them!


Tools for Crimping Wire Ferrules

American Electrical has a wide range of low cost, high quality   hand, pneumatic and automatic tools for crimping wire ferrules, stripping and   cutting wire.






DIN Rail

We offer a complete line of slotted or solid DIN Rail - 35 mm   x 15 mm, 35 mm x 7.5 mm) in 1 or 2 meter lengths. DIN Rail mounts in a variety   of enclosures and junction boxes.




DIN Rail Mounted Interface Modules

The American Electrical Interface Modules are available with   D-sub or IDC connectors, enabling users to attach field wiring and "plug and   play" the Module to the controller. We offer the cables as well.


DIN Rail Mounted Disconnect Switches 

American Electrical has two series of disconnect switches,   ranging from 16 A to 125 A. Isolation of control equipment is an important   design consideration. 




Cable Grips

American Electrical offers the AGRO line of NPT, PG and Metric   - Nylon and Nickel-plated Brass Cable Grips. 

                                Additional information can   be obtained from the Agro website at Agro




Printed Circuit Board Terminal Blocks and Connectors

American Electrical offers Terminal Blocks and Connectors for   the PCB – from 3.5mm up to 7.62mm in various orientations to solve any   application need.


Screwdrivers

American Electrical offers insulated and non-insulated   screwdrivers with a nice ergonomic design allowing the user to properly torque   screws for a vibration-proof application.











