Online Payment Options

Free Payment with Checking Account

Must be enrolled in paperless billing. View benefits about paperless billing
Free immediate payment now available. More details payment notification
Payments can also be scheduled in advance (allow 2 business days).


Benefits of Paperless Billing

Pay your bills online for free from your checking account – immediate payment option now available
Help the environment by using less paper
Receive email notification when your bill is ready
Enjoy convenience – get online access
                to all of your bills

Sign Up Now
×


Free Immediate Online Payments
AEP Ohio will be immediately notified
			of your payment through an electronic memo posting to your electric account. Payments
			received prior to 4:00 p.m. EST will be posted to your account the next AEP Ohio business day. Payments
			made after 4:00 p.m. EST, on a weekend, or on a holiday will take up to 2 business days to post.



Pay By Credit / Debit Card (w/ Fee)

Pay immediately by credit, debit, some ATM cards, electronic check (Business customers: electronic check only).	
        
$2.95 fee collected by our partner BillMatrix.
			More details BillMatrix payments


The service fee will be charged by the service provider, BillMatrix. 
						While you will be paying your account with 
						AEP Ohio, the full amount of the fee is
						passed to BillMatrix as the provider of this service. If you have any questions or problems with your payment, please contact BillMatrix at 1-800-611-0964.


                    You will receive a confirmation code as proof of payment.
					AEP Ohio will be immediately notified
					of your payment through an electronic memo posting to your electric account. Payments
					received prior to 4:00 p.m. EST will be posted to your account that evening. Those
					made after 4:00 p.m. EST, on a weekend, or on a holiday will post on the next
					AEP Ohio business day. Posting schedules
					may vary on holidays.
                

                    Once you have used this service, you can check your
					AEP Ohio account balances and initiate
					payments 24 hours a day, seven days a week. However, using this payment option one
					month does not obligate you to pay this way every month.
                
×


Payments cannot be scheduled in advance.
You'll need your account number. Login to get it.
			




