Welcome to American Electric Company Inc
     
American Electric Company Inc, your authorized Generac Generator dealer!
As a Generac Authorized dealer, American Electric Company Inc of Draper, UT brings you peace of mind with a full line of reliable Generac products backed by world-class service and support. Explore our product selection. Then contact us so we can help you select the Generac solution that's just right for you.

Emergency power systems that can back up your entire home or business, or just the most essential circuits.
Portable power products that let you take your electricity where you need it most, whether it’s a tailgate party or a construction site.
Power washers that make it easy to tackle even your toughest cleaning projects.

American Electric Company Inc is an Authorized GOAL ZERO Dealer, ask us about all the great products available. We have excellent pricing and off-grid solutions available.
American Electrical Company Inc., is a full-service electrical construction, service and maintenance company. Our company has many years’ experience in commercial, residential, industrial and renovation work. We offer design-build services including emergency and standby power generation to integrate with your new and existing systems. American Electric has been in business for 41 years as a family owned and operated business.  American Electric is bondable and insured; we hold electrical and general construction licenses in Utah, Wyoming, Idaho, Nevada and Washington.
American Electric has been in business since 1972 and we have the knowledge and experience to offer quality work at a competitive price.
Licenses and Certifications:

Electrical and general construction license for Utah
Electrical license for Wyoming, Idaho, Nevada and Washington
Member of IEC of Utah (Independent Electrical Contractors of Utah)- have served and currently serve in management positions
Multiple factory trained Generac service personnel
Committed to safety and continuing education


